1. Modify test_builder/build.xml.
    - Set eclipse-home's value.
2. Export "kr.or.tyson.yamlbot" to eclipse-home's plugins folder.
3. Modify context in "kr.or.tyson.yamlbot/test.script".
4. Copy "test_builder/plugins" to eclipse-home's plugins directory.
6. Just execute "ant" in test_builder.
